---
title: Middle Eastern Beef Tagine with Garlic Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Take a little bit of chermoula spice, some flavoursome diced beef and a sprinkling of currants for sweetness, and what have you
got? Why, it’s the perfect recipe for a delicious beef and couscous tagine!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-beef-tagine-c9c62673.jpg
